Body:
Description: EPP is causing the Proton VPN Client from failing an SSO sign in via Okta.

Sign in works without issue when EPP Client has been removed.

What We've Learned Updated: 20/05/2025
Client claims the EPP client is preventing them from accessing the Proton VPN through SSO.

Next Steps Updated: 20/05/2025
Will have to investigate further.
